{"word":"φιλοφροσύνη","slug":"φιλοφροσύνη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>φιλοφροσύνη</b></el> <el>(φῐλοφροσύνη, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:φιλόφρων'><el>φιλόφρων</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>friendliness, kindliness</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <el>τινός</el> <i>towards</i> one, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>πρός τινα</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>: <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <i>friendly greetings</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>cheerfulness</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}